<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Math Tutoring | Expert Instruction</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 font-sans">

    <header class="bg-white shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-50">
        <nav class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">MATH TUTORING</span>
            <a href="#contact" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition">Book a Session</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">Master Mathematics with <span class="text-blue-600">Precision</span>.</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Providing 5+ years of expert tutoring in Calculus, Statistics, and Data Analysis for university and high school students.</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="#services" class="border border-gray-300 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">View Subjects</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="bg-gray-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-black transition">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="bg-white py-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Specialized Expertise</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="p-8 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Calculus</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">From limits to multivariable integration, focusing on the "why" behind the theorems.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Statistics</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Probability distributions, hypothesis testing, and data modeling for advanced coursework.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Test Prep</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Strategic preparation for standardized exams and professional quantitative certifications.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to improve your grade?</h2>
        <p class="mb-10 text-gray-600">In-person (local) and Zoom sessions available. Standard rates start at $60/hr.</p>
        <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600 underline">Email to Inquire</a>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-10 text-center text-gray-400 text-sm">
        &copy; 2026 Math Tutoring Services. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
